text: "One Summer" is a 1989 song by Australian singer Daryl Braithwaite and is the third single from his second studio album Edge. It went to number 8 in Australia, number 4 in Sweden and number 5 in Norway. == Track listing == *Side A "One Summer" – 3:42 *Side B "Pretending to Care" – 3:39 Category:1989 songs Category:Pop songs
title: One Summer (song)
